      "# 直接访问列\nprint(df3['name'])\n# loc：选择列范围\nprint(df3.loc[:, 'name':'num'])\n# iloc：按位置选择列\nprint(df3.iloc[:, 1])\n```",
      "### 行和列结合",
      "同时操作行和列：",
      "```python\n# 用字典创建 DataFrame\nimport pandas as pd",
