      "筛选num大于30的name",
      "```python\n# 用字典创建 DataFrame\nimport pandas as pd",
      "data = {'name': ['apple', 'egg', 'watermelon'],\n        'color': ['red', 'yellow', 'green'],\n        'num': [30, 40, 50]}\ndf3 = pd.DataFrame(data, index=['No.1', 'No.2', 'No.3'])\n# 筛选 num > 30 的行的 name 列\nprint(df3['name'][df3['num'] > 30])\n```",
      "## 修改 DataFrame",
      "### 添加列",
