      "data = {'name': ['apple', 'egg', 'watermelon'],\n        'color': ['red', 'yellow', 'green'],\n        'num': [30, 40, 50]}\ndf3 = pd.DataFrame(data, index=['No.1', 'No.2', 'No.3'])\ndf3.drop('No.3', inplace=True)\nprint(df3)\n```",
      "删除列",
      "使用 del（直接修改原数据）：",
      "```\n# 用字典创建 DataFrame\nimport pandas as pd",
      "data = {'name': ['apple', 'egg', 'watermelon'],\n        'color': ['red', 'yellow', 'green'],\n        'num': [30, 40, 50]}\ndf3 = pd.DataFrame(data, index=['No.1', 'No.2', 'No.3'])\ndel df3['num']\nprint(df3)\n```",
      "使用 drop（需指定 axis=1）：",
      "```python\n# 用字典创建 DataFrame\nimport pandas as pd",
      "data = {'name': ['apple', 'egg', 'watermelon'],\n        'color': ['red', 'yellow', 'green'],\n        'num': [30, 40, 50]}\ndf3 = pd.DataFrame(data, index=['No.1', 'No.2', 'No.3'])\ndf3.drop('num', axis=1, inplace=True)\nprint(df3)\n```",
      "## 读取和写入文件",
      "**从 CSV 读取**",
