      "## 代码",
      "```cpp\nclass Solution {\npublic:\n    int findPeakElement(vector& nums) {\n        int left = -1, right = nums.size() - 1; // 开区间 (-1, n-1)\n        while (left + 1  nums[mid + 1]) {\n                right = mid; // 峰值可能在左半段或 mid 处\n            } else {\n                left = mid;  // 峰值必在右半段\n            }\n        }\n        return right; // 最终 right 指向峰值\n    }\n};\n```",
